title: The ballot boxes in Arkansas Typo put the name Liar in the name of Hillary Clinton.
subtitle: The first name Hillary Clinton was spelled "Helliari" in the 2016 elections and the ballot papers were printed for use in Lonoke County, Arkansas.
author: David Emery
vclaim: The first name Hillary Clinton was spelled "Helliari" on the ballot papers printed for use in Lonoke County, Arkansas.
